high_descs: Turn around, walk straight and turn to the right to go to the dishwasher.
Pick up a potato next to the green cup on the table.
Walk to the right and turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the potato next to the tomato in the fridge, close the fridge, let it cool for a while, pick it up again and close the fridge.
Go to the microwave on the counter top next to the fridge.
Put the potato in it and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the microwave next to the fridge.

high_descs: Walk over to the microwave on the counter.
Pick up the potato that is on the front edge of the counter in front of you.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge for a couple seconds to let it get cold, then take it out and close the fridge.
Walk back over to the microwave.
Put the chilled potato in the microwave then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, and turn left again and head towards the sink, then turn right and go to the counter
Pick up the cookie from the counter
Turn right and go to the fridge
Put the cookie into the fridge and wait a bit, then take the cookie out of the fridge
Turn left and head towards the sink then turn right and go to the microwave
Put the cookie in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cookie into the microwave
